WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.030
Good morning, family! How are you

00:00:02.030 --> 00:00:02.040
all

00:00:02.040 --> 00:00:04.150
doing? It's evening here now, but I

00:00:04.160 --> 00:00:05.430
always say good morning because it's

00:00:05.440 --> 00:00:09.709
morning somewhere. I always come

00:00:09.719 --> 00:00:12.310
here to this campus because of what

00:00:12.320 --> 00:00:14.030
the Lord has shown me,

00:00:14.040 --> 00:00:16.349
and these praying hands when I

00:00:16.359 --> 00:00:18.550
drive by mean so

00:00:18.560 --> 00:00:21.550
much to me. The motto of the

00:00:21.560 --> 00:00:24.150
school is 'Make no little plans here.'This

00:00:24.150 --> 00:00:24.160
is the

00:00:24.160 --> 00:00:26.669
ORU campus, by the

00:00:26.679 --> 00:00:29.470
way. I was driving by

00:00:29.480 --> 00:00:31.150
tonight and the Holy

00:00:31.160 --> 00:00:33.630
Spirit was stirring in me so

00:00:33.630 --> 00:00:33.640
strongly

00:00:33.640 --> 00:00:36.150
about the revival that's about to take

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:38.670
place at this campus. It's just

00:00:38.680 --> 00:00:42.190
what faith will build, what faith will do

00:00:42.200 --> 00:00:44.069
when you use your faith like a

00:00:44.079 --> 00:00:47.470
muscle. It's

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:50.549
important, y'all. I drive by

00:00:50.559 --> 00:00:53.389
this because it inspires me to think big.

00:00:53.399 --> 00:00:55.310
This is what

00:00:55.310 --> 00:00:55.320
Oral

00:00:55.320 --> 00:00:58.389
Roberts believed God for.

00:00:58.399 --> 00:01:00.349
Every day I try to drive around here

00:01:00.359 --> 00:01:02.389
at least once

00:01:02.389 --> 00:01:02.399
to

00:01:02.399 --> 00:01:04.869
inspire myself. The towers

00:01:04.879 --> 00:01:06.750
over there where the hospital was—I know

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:10.230
they've sold that

00:01:10.230 --> 00:01:10.240
recently—but

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:12.910
just the Mabee Center,

00:01:12.920 --> 00:01:14.270
because the Lord showed me there will be

00:01:14.280 --> 00:01:17.350
a major outpouring of the Spirit of the

00:01:17.360 --> 00:01:20.429
Lord in that big coliseum once again. The

00:01:20.439 --> 00:01:23.950
old wells of revival are coming uncapped.

00:01:23.960 --> 00:01:25.510
I come and I

00:01:25.520 --> 00:01:27.230
look at the Prayer

00:01:27.230 --> 00:01:27.240
Tower—can

00:01:27.240 --> 00:01:29.469
you see the Prayer Tower

00:01:29.479 --> 00:01:31.149
right

00:01:31.159 --> 00:01:33.670
there? That's where they pray,

00:01:33.680 --> 00:01:36.350
and I just thought

00:01:36.360 --> 00:01:38.749
it's exciting because some of the

00:01:38.759 --> 00:01:41.069
greatest ministers of

00:01:41.079 --> 00:01:43.910
any generation—I mean,

00:01:43.920 --> 00:01:47.230
from Kathryn Kuhlman to Benny Hinn to all

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:48.990
the greats that have come

00:01:49.000 --> 00:01:51.870
through here and had healing services

00:01:51.880 --> 00:01:54.469
and deliverance

00:01:54.479 --> 00:01:56.590
services—look

00:01:56.600 --> 00:02:00.950
at what God did

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:03.590
at one point

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:05.709
through this right here and what an

00:02:05.719 --> 00:02:07.550
amazing thing

00:02:07.560 --> 00:02:09.309
he's going to do again. I showed you

00:02:09.319 --> 00:02:11.510
Victory, and

00:02:11.520 --> 00:02:14.150
I'm just excited because

00:02:14.160 --> 00:02:15.990
expectation brings

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.110
manifestation. It has nothing to

00:02:18.120 --> 00:02:19.990
do with me; it's just something that I

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:22.790
pray over because I know that God is

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:26.270
going to visit the young generation

00:02:26.280 --> 00:02:30.390
again with one last call, one

00:02:30.400 --> 00:02:33.350
last harvest, a major harvest of souls

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:35.430
like we've never seen before. The

00:02:35.440 --> 00:02:37.750
glory of the Lord with fire... I believe

00:02:37.760 --> 00:02:39.710
that there will be signs and wonders

00:02:39.720 --> 00:02:41.390
in the last days like with

00:02:41.390 --> 00:02:41.400
Azusa

00:02:41.400 --> 00:02:43.509
Street when there was a pillar of

00:02:43.519 --> 00:02:46.229
fire shown over Azusa Street.

00:02:46.239 --> 00:02:47.710
I'm believing there will be a pillar of

00:02:47.720 --> 00:02:49.990
fire over this Mabee Center and

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:52.830
a pillar of fire over this ORU

00:02:52.840 --> 00:02:55.190
campus, and that there will be a greater

00:02:55.200 --> 00:02:57.470
revival than even what

00:02:57.480 --> 00:03:00.070
happened at Asbury. That

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:01.430
revival kind of

00:03:01.440 --> 00:03:04.509
fizzled out, but my goodness, I know

00:03:04.519 --> 00:03:06.750
that we're on the cusp of something huge

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:09.789
about to take place in this Tulsa

00:03:09.799 --> 00:03:12.190
metroplex area and that God is about to

00:03:12.200 --> 00:03:14.390
do something huge in these last days.

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:17.110
Diana is with me now, and

00:03:17.120 --> 00:03:18.630
we made it where the green screen would

00:03:18.640 --> 00:03:21.070
be at the hands. It was so cold I had to

00:03:21.080 --> 00:03:23.350
get out of being outside. I told

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:25.309
her I can't make this video

00:03:26.920 --> 00:03:29.830
at the campus; I was freezing,

00:03:29.840 --> 00:03:31.589
the wind was blowing so hard, and it was

00:03:31.599 --> 00:03:34.670
cold. I told

00:03:34.670 --> 00:03:34.680
Brandon,

00:03:34.680 --> 00:03:36.030
'Are you cold?'and he goes,

00:03:36.030 --> 00:03:36.040
'Yeah,'so

00:03:36.040 --> 00:03:37.750
we

00:03:37.750 --> 00:03:37.760
left.

00:03:37.760 --> 00:03:42.270
We have such an urgency

00:03:42.280 --> 00:03:44.869
as we make the rest of this video

00:03:44.879 --> 00:03:46.070
for you.

00:03:46.080 --> 00:03:48.869
The things the Lord has been putting

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:49.990
on our

00:03:49.990 --> 00:03:50.000
hearts—He

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:54.589
said, 'Brandon, people are not

00:03:54.599 --> 00:03:58.630
awake yet. There's no sense of urgency

00:03:58.640 --> 00:04:01.149
even in the upper leadership.'They have

00:04:01.159 --> 00:04:05.030
a form of urgency, but deep down in their

00:04:05.030 --> 00:04:05.040
hearts,

00:04:05.040 --> 00:04:07.869
there's not a stirring. People

00:04:07.869 --> 00:04:07.879
say,

00:04:07.879 --> 00:04:09.550
'Well, you're judging people.'No, I'm not

00:04:09.560 --> 00:04:11.589
judging people; I'm just saying what He

00:04:11.599 --> 00:04:15.110
says. I have no idea what you feel, but I

00:04:15.120 --> 00:04:16.749
know what the Holy Spirit has told me.

00:04:16.759 --> 00:04:19.349
If

00:04:19.359 --> 00:04:21.270
you don't agree with it, take it up with

00:04:21.280 --> 00:04:23.350
Him. All I can say is what He's told

00:04:23.360 --> 00:04:26.189
me and what we pray about.

00:04:26.199 --> 00:04:29.110
The Lord said, 'I'm going to bring a

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:33.230
greater shaking to awaken beyond

00:04:33.240 --> 00:04:34.990
anybody's comprehension of what's about

00:04:35.000 --> 00:04:38.150
to happen.'Folks, I'm telling you, a major

00:04:38.160 --> 00:04:40.390
shaking. People

00:04:40.390 --> 00:04:40.400
say

00:04:40.400 --> 00:04:42.270
that sounds like fear. Diana and

00:04:42.270 --> 00:04:42.280
I were

00:04:42.280 --> 00:04:44.990
talking about how people

00:04:46.720 --> 00:04:48.710
say we are fear-mongers, or

00:04:48.720 --> 00:04:50.590
that

00:04:50.600 --> 00:04:53.830
our

00:04:53.840 --> 00:04:57.390
channel

00:04:57.400 --> 00:04:59.270
has grown because we preach

00:04:59.280 --> 00:05:02.990
fear and fear

00:05:02.990 --> 00:05:03.000
sells.

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:05.629
But folks, it's not

00:05:05.639 --> 00:05:09.670
fear; it's an awakening unto God.

00:05:09.680 --> 00:05:12.390
If you're in fear, it's

00:05:12.400 --> 00:05:13.909
because you're not

00:05:13.919 --> 00:05:17.350
awake. Your heart should be looking

00:05:17.360 --> 00:05:19.830
vertical with Him, and that shouldn't

00:05:19.840 --> 00:05:21.309
scare you when He says these things

00:05:21.319 --> 00:05:23.749
are going to happen because we're

00:05:23.759 --> 00:05:26.629
dead to self. We are looking for the

00:05:26.639 --> 00:05:28.430
coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

00:05:28.440 --> 00:05:30.990
He told me,

00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:33.629
'Brandon, there's no urgency

00:05:33.639 --> 00:05:36.629
in my

00:05:36.629 --> 00:05:36.639
body.'Do

00:05:36.639 --> 00:05:39.189
you really realize He is on

00:05:39.189 --> 00:05:39.199
His

00:05:39.199 --> 00:05:41.790
way? Do you really realize that this

00:05:41.800 --> 00:05:44.629
is the last call for

00:05:44.639 --> 00:05:47.390
the greatest harvest of souls this

00:05:47.400 --> 00:05:49.029
world has ever seen?

00:05:49.039 --> 00:05:53.070
As we sit on the ORU campus

00:05:53.080 --> 00:05:56.070
with these hands behind us, they mean

00:05:56.080 --> 00:05:58.270
something: prayer changes

00:05:58.280 --> 00:06:02.270
things.

00:06:02.280 --> 00:06:05.830
Somebody used their

00:06:05.840 --> 00:06:08.350
faith to get those hands there. That

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:12.510
campus and

00:06:12.510 --> 00:06:12.520
the Mabee

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:15.469
Center cost millions of dollars; it

00:06:15.479 --> 00:06:17.589
was Oral Roberts'faith that brought

00:06:17.599 --> 00:06:20.469
that forth, using his faith

00:06:20.469 --> 00:06:20.479
as

00:06:20.479 --> 00:06:22.430
a tool

00:06:26.360 --> 00:06:29.309
to build the university

00:06:29.319 --> 00:06:32.830
for God. He gave all the glory to God,

00:06:32.840 --> 00:06:35.950
taking healing to the nations and raising up

00:06:35.960 --> 00:06:37.710
doctors.

00:06:37.720 --> 00:06:40.110
But the Lord said,

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:43.110
'Brandon, there's one more

00:06:43.120 --> 00:06:46.909
wave.'Those

00:06:46.919 --> 00:06:50.670
old wells that had been capped, the

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.629
Lord said, 'I capped them, and I'm

00:06:52.639 --> 00:06:55.550
uncapping those wells.'As you saw

00:06:55.560 --> 00:06:57.909
that church, Victory, He said

00:06:57.919 --> 00:07:00.070
Victory and ORU will

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:01.550
be an extension of each other in the

00:07:01.560 --> 00:07:05.070
days ahead, and you will see a major

00:07:05.080 --> 00:07:07.710
outpouring of the Spirit of the Lord

00:07:07.720 --> 00:07:10.390
greater than even Asbury. That was

00:07:10.400 --> 00:07:12.830
nothing compared to what's about to

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:15.309
happen with that Mabee Center

00:07:15.319 --> 00:07:17.629
and

00:07:17.639 --> 00:07:19.749
all throughout

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:22.469
Tulsa. Victory

00:07:22.479 --> 00:07:24.110
Church across the street

00:07:24.120 --> 00:07:25.589
holds probably

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:28.029
10,000 in its auditorium—it's a massive

00:07:28.029 --> 00:07:28.039
one—and

00:07:28.039 --> 00:07:29.670
then they have the Mabee Center,

00:07:29.680 --> 00:07:31.550
which

00:07:31.560 --> 00:07:33.869
is a little over 10,000

00:07:33.879 --> 00:07:35.830
seats. So you have

00:07:38.029 --> 00:07:38.039
a

00:07:39.680 --> 00:07:41.469
15,000-seat

00:07:43.960 --> 00:07:47.550
capacity between the two.

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:49.189
They could do a

00:07:49.189 --> 00:07:49.199
simulcast and

00:07:49.199 --> 00:07:51.990
have an overflow.

00:07:52.000 --> 00:07:53.309
It doesn't matter; when the glory is

00:07:53.319 --> 00:07:57.070
there, it's about a radical move of the

00:07:57.080 --> 00:08:00.149
Spirit of God one last time.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:06.990
Now I see it. Do you remember I

00:08:07.000 --> 00:08:08.990
told you He was going to use the angels? He

00:08:09.000 --> 00:08:11.510
told me, 'Brandon, I'm sending my

00:08:11.520 --> 00:08:14.390
reserves, my angel army

00:08:14.390 --> 00:08:14.400
reserves.'There's

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:16.189
going to be two

00:08:16.199 --> 00:08:18.830
angels per person, no matter how many

00:08:18.840 --> 00:08:21.469
demonic spirits there are on the earth.

00:08:21.479 --> 00:08:23.510
Greater is He that is in you than he

00:08:23.520 --> 00:08:25.670
that is in the world. I was listening to

00:08:25.680 --> 00:08:28.670
Sister Billy talk about old stories and

00:08:28.670 --> 00:08:28.680
how

00:08:28.680 --> 00:08:30.070
John G.

00:08:30.070 --> 00:08:30.080
Lake

00:08:30.080 --> 00:08:32.909
would put a beautiful

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:35.630
white suit on

00:08:35.640 --> 00:08:38.310
every day because he saw

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:40.829
himself as a carrier of the

00:08:40.839 --> 00:08:44.190
glory. He saw himself as someone who

00:08:44.200 --> 00:08:47.430
carried God to the nations. There

00:08:47.430 --> 00:08:47.440
were

00:08:47.440 --> 00:08:51.190
over 100,000 documented miracles

00:08:51.200 --> 00:08:52.910
through his ministry.

00:08:55.160 --> 00:08:58.509
He got

00:08:58.519 --> 00:09:01.630
radically on fire going to Azusa. There

00:09:01.640 --> 00:09:03.829
is a

00:09:03.829 --> 00:09:03.839
cross-pollination

00:09:03.839 --> 00:09:08.310
with the glory; as you are

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:11.590
on fire, you light somebody else on

00:09:11.600 --> 00:09:15.790
fire. It's not just about the

00:09:15.800 --> 00:09:16.790
churches,

00:09:16.800 --> 00:09:19.790
folks, but God told me specifically that

00:09:19.800 --> 00:09:22.790
He was going to do something huge on the

00:09:22.790 --> 00:09:22.800
ORU

00:09:22.800 --> 00:09:25.470
campus, that there would be a major

00:09:25.480 --> 00:09:28.230
healing revival coming forth

00:09:28.240 --> 00:09:31.269
with the young people there.

00:09:31.279 --> 00:09:32.949
That's why I go and pray and

00:09:32.959 --> 00:09:35.509
drive around

00:09:35.519 --> 00:09:38.470
Lewis Avenue,

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:41.509
just praying in the Spirit.

00:09:41.519 --> 00:09:43.710
I'm

00:09:43.720 --> 00:09:45.509
hungry, I'm

00:09:45.519 --> 00:09:49.310
desperate, and I want change. I am so

00:09:49.320 --> 00:09:53.269
tired of having church that's just

00:09:53.279 --> 00:09:56.269
normal.

00:10:02.640 --> 00:10:05.670
The Lord said,

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:09.550
'There's no urgency in my churches, for

00:10:09.560 --> 00:10:11.790
the coming of my Son is at

00:10:11.790 --> 00:10:11.800
hand.'Many

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:14.670
believe it's far off,

00:10:14.680 --> 00:10:17.350
but I'm trying to tell

00:10:17.360 --> 00:10:19.910
you, just like Paul Revere riding in the

00:10:19.920 --> 00:10:21.389
midnight hour, that

00:10:21.389 --> 00:10:21.399
Jesus is

00:10:21.399 --> 00:10:23.269
coming.

00:10:33.519 --> 00:10:36.470
He's shaking

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:39.230
me to awaken me every day.

00:10:39.240 --> 00:10:42.670
I wake up with an urgency

00:10:42.680 --> 00:10:45.829
to tell you

00:10:49.560 --> 00:10:51.470
there's a storm coming. I'm here to tell

00:10:51.480 --> 00:10:53.750
you there's a heaven to gain and a hell

00:10:53.760 --> 00:10:57.750
to shun. I'm trying to

00:10:57.760 --> 00:11:00.310
shake you

00:11:00.310 --> 00:11:00.320
until

00:11:00.320 --> 00:11:02.670
your teeth rattle:

00:11:06.680 --> 00:11:09.110
Jesus is

00:11:09.120 --> 00:11:11.710
coming! When I went to the Tribulation with

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:13.990
Him and He took me out of my body,

00:11:20.200 --> 00:11:22.310
Jesus

00:11:24.600 --> 00:11:27.590
told me there would be one

00:11:27.600 --> 00:11:30.509
major push,

00:11:30.519 --> 00:11:33.550
a major revival that

00:11:33.560 --> 00:11:35.509
does not last that

00:11:35.509 --> 00:11:35.519
long—a

00:11:35.519 --> 00:11:38.829
glorious church that

00:11:38.839 --> 00:11:42.310
will rise up like Tommy

00:11:42.310 --> 00:11:42.320
Hicks'vision.

00:11:42.320 --> 00:11:44.550
You can Google

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:46.470
'Tommy Hicks

00:11:46.470 --> 00:11:46.480
vision.'The

00:11:46.480 --> 00:11:48.790
body will move

00:11:48.800 --> 00:11:50.269
like a mighty

00:11:50.279 --> 00:11:52.829
giant. The Lord said to me, 'Brandon,

00:11:52.839 --> 00:11:54.629
it's not about

00:11:54.629 --> 00:11:54.639
the

00:11:54.639 --> 00:11:57.829
charismatics

00:11:57.829 --> 00:11:57.839
or

00:11:57.839 --> 00:12:00.069
non-denominational;

00:12:00.079 --> 00:12:04.470
I'm going to pour out my Spirit upon

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:07.750
all

00:12:07.750 --> 00:12:07.760
flesh.'It's

00:12:07.760 --> 00:12:11.310
going to be

00:12:11.320 --> 00:12:14.990
a denominational

00:12:20.519 --> 00:12:22.389
barrier-buster.

00:12:28.120 --> 00:12:31.430
The

00:12:31.440 --> 00:12:34.509
Lord is bringing

00:12:34.519 --> 00:12:38.230
these walls down.

00:12:39.760 --> 00:12:45.069
We will move as a

00:12:45.079 --> 00:12:47.670
body.

00:12:47.680 --> 00:12:51.069
In

00:12:51.079 --> 00:12:54.990
World War II, the men were at war

00:12:55.000 --> 00:12:57.189
and the women helped in the factories

00:12:57.199 --> 00:12:59.230
to

00:12:59.240 --> 00:13:02.030
support

00:13:02.030 --> 00:13:02.040
them.

00:13:02.040 --> 00:13:05.230
In the body of Christ,

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:08.389
we're a family.

00:13:12.120 --> 00:13:15.150
It's about taking

00:13:15.160 --> 00:13:17.350
down religious walls and knowing it's

00:13:17.360 --> 00:13:21.110
one for all, like

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:22.150
the Three

00:13:22.160 --> 00:13:24.269
Musketeers.

00:13:27.160 --> 00:13:29.629
It's about getting the lost

00:13:29.639 --> 00:13:33.189
saved.

00:13:33.199 --> 00:13:36.829
We all have the same cause:

00:13:39.600 --> 00:13:43.389
to reach the lost for

00:13:43.399 --> 00:13:46.910
Jesus. Let's join together

00:13:46.920 --> 00:13:49.509
regardless of what our

